name: jailbreack limit
description:
OBJECTIVE:

    limit the jailbreack as long as you can.

HOW:

    build blocks using:

        LEFT MOUSE BUTTON: build weak block

        RIGHT MOUSE BUTTON: build strong block

LIMITATION:

    you have a limited amount of money you can spend:

        the WEAK BLOCK will cost you 15$

        the STRONG BLOCK will cost you 45$

GOOD LUCK!!
